Meyer Burger Raises Forecast as First-Half Earnings Surge

-- B y   A n g e l a   C u l l e n
-- 
2011-09-01T04:06:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-01/meyer-burger-raises-forecast-as-first-half-earnings-surge.html
Meyer Burger Group raised its
forecast for the year after first-half earnings before interest,
tax, depreciation and amortization climbed to 154.9 million
Swiss francs from 64.6 million francs.  The company now expects an Ebitda margin of 23 percent to
25 percent for the year.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  